 That the State's mediation program provides mediation services
to covered persons with the aim of reaching mutually agreeable
decisions between the parties under the program;

 That the State's mediation program is authorized or
administered by an agency of the State government or by the Governor
of the State;

 That the State's mediation program provides for training of
mediators in mediation skills and in all issues covered by the
State's mediation program;

 That the State's mediation program ensures, in the case of
agricultural loans, that all lenders and borrowers of agricultural
loans receive adequate notification of the mediation program;

